entries.femaleVariant: Hello, V.
Need to talk.
It's not Holt. You're being brainwashed.
Don't have much to add.
SSI wasn't working for Holt. You're in deeper shit than you think.
entries.maleVariant: SSI wasn't workin' for Holt. You're in deeper shit than you think.

entries.femaleVariant: Strange as it may sound, don't got much.
There's got to be something. You didn't find any hard evidence?
What do you plan to do?
Elizabeth knows everything.
Your wife knows everything.
Liz? How?
Figured it out at some point.
Elizabeth? No. No, no, no... she would've said something.
So what now? Ya still wanna be mayor?
I'll wait – for my window, an opportunity – then make my move.
Well, I'm not about to give up. I didn't run just to… ehh...
Good luck.
And good night.
Isn't that exactly what they want?
Oh, I'll give 'em more than they bargained for. Yeah, same with your eddies... Take care, V.
Yes, I know. Elizabeth filled me in.
She feared for your life, your daughter's life. Who could blame her?
Got an anonymous holo tellin' her to keep her mouth shut. So she did what the perfect candidate's wife would do – protected her family.
Hate to say this, but... I think the whole situation was convenient.
Think about it... Perfect wife of the perfect mayor... That's who they conditioned her to be.
She must've believed she was protecting Xochi... and me. Would've told me otherwise.
Nah. No, she's never kept anything from me. And she doesn't scare easily, believe me.
I won't let them get away with this…
Convenient? This is my wife you're talking about.
She was protecting you.
It was convenient not to.
Sounds like I was right to hire a professional.
SSI was taking money from Holt.
If only corpses could talk.
Sorry, it's all hearsay and speculation.
Well, one thing led to another and some lead was fired.
Mh. Burned to a crisp in their own van. Managed to squeeze one of 'em before…
entries.maleVariant: Yeah. Burned to a crisp in their own van. Managed to squeeze one of 'em before, uh…

entries.femaleVariant: He confessed, but his word isn't worth jack now.
Like what?
SSI took money from all kinds of people, Holt among them.
But it's a weak lead. Too weak. Nothing that can help you,  Jefferson.
entries.maleVariant: But it's a weak lead... too weak. Nothing that can help you,  Jefferson.

entries.femaleVariant: No shit. Between you and those... spies?
Damn. All right, I'll handle things from here.
Meaning?
First, I'm gonna win this damn election.
Then I'll find the motherfucker who spied on us, and if it was Holt...
Well, then… good luck.
You'll get your fee soon... You already got my gratitude. Goodbye, V.
Meaning?
Elizabeth – what'd she tell you, exactly?
Didn't get specific. Just that SSI was spying for that son of a bitch, Holt.
Guess you got more, though?
They're in your heads, pierced your brains.
They're in your heads, Jefferson. Yours and Elizabeth's.
Isn't it weird that you're a virtuous politician, candidate?
I'm not paying you to make up riddles for me. So get to the point.
You never will.
Trust me, you never will.
Got no idea how we'd go about doing that.
First I'll find him, then I'll find whoever's behind this.
Don't count on it – they're too powerful.
You kidding? How would you expect to do that?
entries.maleVariant: You kiddin'? How would you expect to do that?

entries.femaleVariant: Could show their hand if you're patient, wait long enough.
entries.maleVariant: Could show their hand if you're patient, and wait long enough.

entries.femaleVariant: Worst thing anyone can do to a person is strip them of their sense of self. I'd fight back, too.
My god... I have to tell Liz!
You're a virtuous politician. Doesn't that make you wonder?
Hehh, flattered, but no, I'm far from it. Though I try my best. W-what's this got to do with anything?
How many people can honestly say they don't strike deals with gangs or take eddies from corps?
A lot, I'd like to think. They just haven't introduced themselves yet.
Almost like this city doesn't deserve somebody like you…
entries.maleVariant: Almost like this city doesn't deserve someone like you…

entries.femaleVariant: This some kinda chuckle-worthy metaphor?
Strange dreams, partial recall, jumbled memories – it's not just stress and long hours.
I don't know what you're trying to tell me, but I don't think I like where this is heading.
Wake up. Your brain's a mess, messier than the discount section of a BD smut hut.
SSI's on the take of some unknown group that's out to control your lives.
No idea how to go about doing that.
Could show themselves, inadvertently, if you're patient.
I'd try facing up to 'em, too.
Wanna take on a shadowy organization that controls your mind? Anticipates your every move, programs it?
Or use your mayoral powers if you get elected. Long as you don't forget all this by morning…
entries.maleVariant: Or use your mayoral powers if you get elected. As long as you don't forget all this by mornin'…

entries.femaleVariant: Good luck.
So, thoughts?
Hm, somehow I doubt it's people who're behind this.
Very funny. You're too young to remember this, but not so long ago people talked about rogue AIs prowling cyberspace.
So... not aliens?
Doesn't matter who. What matters is that guy decided to take up the gauntlet.
My man.
Someone's conditioning you, remotely.
Somebody's hijacked your life, reset your course, your career.
They want you as their mayor.
Somebody's programming you and your wife.
Sounds like something out of the movies.
Saw your brain scans – they're tweaking your neural connections. This ain't no movie, Jeff.
Your memories – can't even trust those anymore.
entries.maleVariant: Your memories – you can't even trust those anymore.

entries.femaleVariant: I'll admit there were a couple of fortunate coincidences, but it… ehh...
They forged your views, personality, even that skepticism that pisses me off so much.
Clearly what they want is for you to be "their" mayor. Molding you like a clay figurine.
Been at it for a while with you and Liz. Editing your memories, your tastes, your views and beliefs, even.
entries.maleVariant: Been at it for a while, you and Liz. Editing your memories, your tastes, your views and beliefs, even.

entries.femaleVariant: Wait, the intruder. I have to find him!
I-i-if that's true, I'll never know what's real in my life and what's a lie, fabricated…
How could I not have known about this?
Fuck... I need to remember who recommended SSI to me…
Know there's a concealed room in your pad?
entries.maleVariant: You know there's a concealed room in your pad?

entries.femaleVariant: Out with it.
They've got tech in there you wouldn't believe.
These people know everything about you and your wife. Watching your every move.
entries.maleVariant: These people know everything about you and your wife. They're watching your every move.

entries.femaleVariant: Huhh...
Know anything about the concealed room in your apartment?
Pull the curtain back on these motherfuckers and show 'em what's what!
There's gotta be a way!
Don't stand a kitten's chance in the dog pound, sorry.
entries.maleVariant: Ya don't stand a kitten's chance in the dog pound, sorry.

entries.femaleVariant: Sun Tzu's "Art of War"? "Feign weakness, so your enemy may grow arrogant."
Don't see you doing much feigning, Jeff…
They've made me a winner, hahaha, and they're going to regret that. For now, I'll let them think they're pulling the strings.
Nope. Don't know anything more.
Nope. Don't know anything more.
So aliens?
[Sit] We need to talk.
I'll find every last speck of dirt on him and bury him under the heap!
So... not aliens?
Doesn't matter who or what. Our guy's outmatched – they can do whatever they want.
He's fucked, V.
Anything else I can do?
Is there anything else I can do?
You've done enough already, V. All that's left to do is wait.
[Stand]
